<plot>A young girl (Amelia), played by Mercedes Quadros, is distressed and feeling guilty about losing the wings she was to wear in her school play. Then she notices an angel and follows the angel into a dark building. Upstairs in the attic, bathed in heavenly light, is an artist's model - the ANGEL. The painter ascends a ladder until he is out of shot - supposedly to heaven-and reappears to restore Amelia's joy with a pair of wings.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?034290</url></doc>
